26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_mspdec_gf100.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31#include <nvif/class.h>
32
33void
34gf100_mspdec_init(struct nvkm_falcon *mspdec)
35{
36 struct nvkm_device *device = mspdec->engine.subdev.device;
37 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x085010, 0x0000fff2);
38 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x08501c, 0x0000fff2);
39}
40
41static const struct nvkm_falcon_func
42gf100_mspdec = {
43 .pmc_enable = 0x00020000,
44 .init = gf100_mspdec_init,
45 .sclass = {
46 { -1, -1, GF100_MSPDEC },
47 {}
48 }
49};
50
51int
52gf100_mspdec_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index,
53 struct nvkm_engine **pengine)
54{
55 return nvkm_mspdec_new_(&gf100_mspdec, device, index, pengine);
56}
